<HEADLINE>
SCENE AT COLONIAL HAS BEEN BIZARRE FOR COURSE
</HEADLINE>
 SCENE-TEX (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By MIKE COCHRAN 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
EDITOR'S NOTE: Star-Telegram writer Mike Cochran, a veteran of 40
years covering the Colonial golf tournament for The Associated
Press, recalls some of the more memorable moments surrounding the
tournament. Throughout the weekend of coverage, Cochran will dcC%1
