Open 9 a.m. to 5 p.m. daily; admission, $4.50.
</P>
<P>
   Next to the Goethe House is the Goethe National Museum, which
features a new, permanent exhibit about Goethe and his time. It
includes manuscripts and letters; $4.50.
</P>
<P>
   Another key stop is the Stadt schloss Museum of contemporary art
