</P>
<P>
   &UR; CONFLICT IN THE BALKANS &LR;   &UR; (i) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   NATO-HUNGARY (Budapest) _ Cracks are beginning to show in
Hungary's commitment to the NATO alliance as the war in Kosovo
grinds on. By Susan Milligan. 800 words.
</P>
<P>
   REFUGEES-BREAD (Kukes, Albania) _ As Adem Kruiziu does daily,
the Kosovar refugee doles out 7 loaves of bread to the 15 relatives
who accompanied him to Kukes six weeks ago. Thousands of refugees
are surviving on cheap, easily deliverable staple. By Lynda Gorov.
1300 words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; INTERNATIONAL (i) &LR;
