<P>
   Hermann Siegel, Arthur ! Jan. 19, 1891 ! Ems ! Ludwigshafen !
France &QL; 
Sternlicht, Lotte ! Dec. 9, 1905 ! Forst ! Dresden ! Belgium &QL; 
Strauss, Emma ! Dec. 26, 1886 ! Wuerzberg ! Munich ! Holland &QL; 
Strauss, Heinrich ! Sept. 8, 1878 ! Unterlaina ! Munich ! Holland &QL; 
Velmann, Walter ! May 4, 1906 ! Altona ! Hamburg ! Holland &QL; 
Zweigenthal, Fritz ! June 8, 1909 ! Vienna ! Vienna ! Belgium &QL;
</P>
</TEXT>
