   ``The Scarlet Pimpernel,'' Minskoff, 200 W. 41st St.
Ticketmaster. 10 and up.
</P>
<P>
   ``The Sound of Music,'' Martin Beck, 302 W. 45th St.
Tele-charge. 6 and up.
</P>
<P>
   ``You're a Good Man, Charlie Brown,'' Ambassador, 219 W. 49th
St. Tele-charge. 8 and up.
</P>
<P>
   _ Paula Crouch Thrasher writes for the Atlanta
Journal-Constitution.
