<HEADER>
A4922 &Cx1f; ttx-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-TEXBUDGET-TEX     05-20 0595
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-TEXBUDGET-TEX </SLUG>
 
 
<TEXT>
<P>
