<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-20 17:25 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5021 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-VIDEO-COLUMN-LADN     05-20 0688
