trainer Bob Baffert bicker about whose horse is better (sort of).
Put your money where your mouth is, Bob Lewis told Bob Baffert this
week. Baffert has a big mouth. Lewis has a lot of money. The best
intentions get caught in the squeeze when top horses are about to
be sent into big races. Friendships last through these things, but
they are tested. Lewis and Baffert are being tested right now.
(Crittenden, Palm Beach Post) MOVED
