</P>
<P>
   THOMPSON-COLUMN (Washington) _ In our obsession with where the
presidential candidates stand in the public opinion polls, we tend
to focus on personality and popularity rather than leadership and
character. By ROBERT E. THOMPSON. (Already filed.)
</P>
