<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-20 20:44 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5253 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SENATE-GUNS-1STLDWRIT     05-20 0993
