5-20 -- Faculty members comfort each other after a shooting at
Heritage High School on Thursday. A student with two guns opened
fire at his school shooting six schoolmates exactly one month after
the Colorado massacre at Columbine High School. The suspect
tearfully surrendered to a school official after putting a gun into
his own mouth. (Alan S. Weiner/The New York Times)
