Spink/Atlanta Journal-Constitution Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT1) CONYERS, Ga. -- May 20, 1999 -- GA-SCHOOL-SHOOTING-1,
05-20 -- Rebecca Harris embraces daughter, Bonnie, a 17-year old
junior. Six students were shot with minor injuries Thursday at
Heritage High School when a student, identified as a Heritage
sophomore, opened fire about 15 minutes before classes were to
begin. Students were in lock down until the suspect was apprehended
and then released to the athletic field where parents reunited with
their children. (John Spink/Atlanta Journal-Constitution Photo)
</P>
<P>
   The New York Times News Service
</P>
</TEXT>
