<P>
   (NYT31) NEW YORK -- May 20, 1999 -- BRITISH-AMERICA, 5-20 --
Heeding the crumpet call at Lady Mendl's Tea Salon in Manhattan.
Much has been made of the fact that British culture has of late
been flooding these shores with almost colonial aplomb. (Ruby
Washington/New York Times Photo) LITE
