investments. (Sal DiMarco Jr./New York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT27) WASHINGTON -- May 20, 1999 -- ADV. FOR SUN., MAY 23 --
BIZ-5-QUESTIONS, 5-20 -- A recent court ruling that some Federal
