<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-20 22:58 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5448 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-RAC-MODESTI-COLUMN-LA     05-20 0882
